Usage: distronomicon [OPTIONS] --app <APP> <COMMAND>

Commands:
  check    Check for updates without installing
  update   Update to the latest release
  version  Show currently installed version
  help     Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
      --repo <REPO>
          GitHub repository (owner/name)
      --app <APP>
          Application name
      --pattern <PATTERN>
          Asset filename pattern (regex)
      --checksum-pattern <CHECKSUM_PATTERN>
          Checksum filename pattern (optional)
      --allow-prerelease
          Allow prerelease versions
      --github-token <GITHUB_TOKEN>
          GitHub API token [env: GITHUB_TOKEN]
      --github-host <GITHUB_HOST>
          GitHub API host [env: GITHUB_HOST=] [default: api.github.com]
      --restart-command <RESTART_COMMAND>
          Command to run after successful update
      --retain <RETAIN>
          Number of releases to retain [default: 3]
      --skip-verification
          Skip checksum verification
      --state-directory <STATE_DIRECTORY>
          State directory [env: STATE_DIRECTORY=]
      --install-root <INSTALL_ROOT>
          Install root directory [env: PREFIX=] [default: /opt]
  -v, --verbose...
          Verbose output (-v, -vv)
  -h, --help
          Print help
